{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id4cef839c-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s11277"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"11277"},"text":"§ 11277.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Evaluation and information","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id4cef839d-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s11277/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" In general","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"If a grantee receives grants for 3 consecutive fiscal years under part A, B, C, D, or E (in the alternative), then the Secretary shall evaluate such grantee on-site, not less frequently than once in the period of such 3 consecutive fiscal years, for purposes of—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id4cef839e-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s11277/a/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" determining whether such grants are being used for the purposes for which such grants are made by the Secretary;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id4cef839f-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s11277/a/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" collecting additional information for the report required by ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t34/s11275"},"text":"section 11275 of this title","children":[],"tail":"; and"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id4cef83a0-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s11277/a/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" providing such information and assistance to such grantee as will enable such grantee to improve the operation of the centers, projects, and activities for which such grants are made.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id4cef83a1-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d","identifier":"/us/usc/t34/s11277/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Cooperation","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Recipients of grants under this subchapter shall cooperate with the Secretary’s efforts to carry out evaluations, and to collect information, under this subchapter.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id4cef83a2-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/93/415/tIII/s386"},"text":"Pub. L. 93–415, title III, § 386","children":[],"tail":", formerly § 364, as added "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/100/690/tVII/s7278"},"text":"Pub. L. 100–690, title VII, § 7278","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1988-11-18"},"text":"Nov. 18, 1988","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/102/4458"},"text":"102 Stat. 4458","children":[],"tail":"; renumbered § 384, "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/586/s3/g/1/A/ii"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–586, § 3(g)(1)(A)(ii)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1992-11-04"},"text":"Nov. 4, 1992","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/106/5022"},"text":"106 Stat. 5022","children":[],"tail":"; renumbered § 386 and amended "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/106/71/s3"},"text":"Pub. L. 106–71, § 3","children":[],"tail":"("},{"tag":"i","attrib":{},"text":"l","children":[],"tail":"), "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1999-10-12"},"text":"Oct. 12, 1999","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/113/1039"},"text":"113 Stat. 1039","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id4cef83a3-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id4cef83a4-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"codification","id":"id4cef83a5-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Codification","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section was formerly classified to ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s5732"},"text":"section 5732 of Title 42","children":[],"tail":", The Public Health and Welfare, prior to editorial reclassification and renumbering as this section."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"id4cef83a6-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1999—","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/106/71"},"text":"Pub. L. 106–71","children":[],"tail":" amended section catchline and text generally. Prior to amendment, text read as follows:"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"“(a) The Secretary shall develop for each fiscal year, and publish annually in the Federal Register for public comment a proposed plan specifying the subject priorities the Secretary will follow in making grants under this subchapter for such fiscal year.","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"“(b) Taking into consideration comments received in the 45-day period beginning on the date the proposed plan is published, the Secretary shall develop and publish, before December 31 of such fiscal year, a final plan specifying the priorities referred to in subsection (a) of this section.”","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"id4cef83a7-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"effectiveDate","id":"id4cef83a8-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Effective Date","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section effective ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1988-10-01"},"text":"Oct. 1, 1988","children":[],"tail":", but not applicable with respect to fiscal year 1989, see section 7296(a), (b)(2) of "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/100/690"},"text":"Pub. L. 100–690","children":[],"tail":", set out as an Effective Date of 1988 Amendment note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t34/s11101"},"text":"section 11101 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
